<collectingCountry box="[1373,1437,2052,2075]" name="Nepal" pageId="17" pageNumber="246">Nepal</collectingCountry>
where the 
<typeStatus box="[262,355,1604,1627]" pageId="18" pageNumber="247">holotype</typeStatus>
was collected. Adjective.
</paragraph>
